title: Purina Beyond Chicken, Carrot and Pea Ground Grain Free Wet Dog Food Natural Pate with Added Vitamins and Minerals - (Pack of 12) 13 oz. Cans
description: Go for real, recognizable ingredients you know and trust and that your dog loves when you bring home this Purina Beyond Grain Free Chicken, Carrot and Pea Recipe Ground Entree adult wet dog food. We purposely select each ingredient in this natural dog food from our trusted sources and add in the vitamins and minerals for the complete and balanced nutrition your adult dog needs to thrive. Real chicken raised without steroids or hormones* is the number 1 ingredient in this high-quality dog food recipe with carrots and peas for wholesome goodness. With natural prebiotic fiber, our high protein wet dog food makes it easy to go Beyond for your pal. We craft our grain free wet dog food with no artificial colors, flavors or preservatives, and we leave out poultry by-product meal, corn, wheat and soy to give your faithful friend the nourishment he needs and nothing he doesn't. *Federal regulations prohibit the use of steroids or hormones in poultry.
